      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRACEFUL WARRIOR (5) lightly raced filly who comes here in peak condition and should appreciate the extra ground. Covered ground early and stuck on gamely to secure third over 1190m at Grafton. Gets map favours today and sure to be thereabouts on the quick back-up. LITERATURE TYCOON (6) drifted back from the sticky gate and gave away a big start before she chipped away late to finish fifth over 1400m at Tamworth. Further improved now and can race a little closer here. Each-way. REAL HOUSEWIVES (8) earlier runs were okay and should appreciate the drop back to 1400m. Assess on her eye-catching third at Tamworth three starts back over this trip. Improver. PINERO (7) ran on late for a plugging third over this trip at Tamworth. Minor place claims again.",
